{"title_page": "Silvia Olmedo", "text_new": "{{short description|TV psychologist and author}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Silvia Olmedo\n| image = Silvia Olmedo Psic\u00f3loga.jpg\n| imagesize = \n| caption = \n| birth_name = Silvia Olmedo\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1976|05|16}}\n| birth_place = [[Madrid]], [[Spain]]\n| occupation = Psychologist, television host, [[writer]], [[lecturer]]\n| yearsactive = \n| website = http://silviaolmedo.com\n}}\n\n'''Silvia Olmedo''' (born 16 May 1976) is a [[Spaniards|Spanish]] [[psychologist]], [[sexologist]], [[Television presenter|television host]], [[Television producer|producer]] and [[author]]. Considered as [https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4206818/0/walter-riso-silvia-olmedo-quienes-son-los-autenticos-influencers-de-la-psicologia-en-redes-sociales/ one of the most influential psychologists in Spanish], she has worked in Spain, [[United States|America]], [[United Kingdom|Britain]], [[Netherlands]], [[Australia]] and [[Mexico]], where she currently hosts a [[television program]] named ''Terapia de Shock''<ref>https://www.canalu.mx/programas/mind-sex</ref> focused on educating people on psychology, sexology and health habits.\n\nSilvia has written five books about psychology, in which she talks about relationships, sexuality, anxiety and self-esteem \u2013 ''Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva'' (''Ask Silvia\u2026Eve's secrets''),<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/preguntale-a-silvia/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> ''Los misterios del amor y el sexo'' (''The Mysteries of Love and Sex'')<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>'', Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos''.,<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/mis-sentimientos-erroneos/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> ''Detox Emocional''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.planetadelibros.com/libro-detox-emocional/206924}}</ref> and ''A dos pasos de la locura (Two steps from Madness)''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/604963/a-dos-pasos-de-la-locura--two-steps-from-madness-by-silvia-olmedo/9781949061413/}}</ref>''.'' All of them became bestsellers, with more than 150,000 copies sold.<ref>http://www.radioformula.com.mx/notas.asp?Idn=466203&idFC=2014/</ref>\n\nBesides her work as a television [[Content (media)|content]] producer and host, she's also dedicated to research in health and mental issues. Silvia is member of the editorial board of ''Women's Health'' magazine. She collaborates with [[Non-governmental organization|NGOs]] such as M\u00e9xico Vivo for education and HIV prevention and is part of the steering committee of Vive Consciente. She is also a well-known lecturer.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tuxtlaenlinea.com/sitio/eventos-2/conferencia-los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo-por-silvia-olmedo/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-12-29 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229050945/http://tuxtlaenlinea.com/sitio/eventos-2/conferencia-los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo-por-silvia-olmedo/ |archivedate=29 December 2014 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nSilvia Olmedo is a content producer and host since 2006. She started at Telelehit with Cuentamelove. She also appears regularly in programs like [[:es:Hoy (programa de televisi\u00f3n)|Hoy]], [[\u00a1Despierta Am\u00e9rica!|Despierta Am\u00e9rica]] and [[Netas Divinas]]. She has also been invited to Primero Noticias, [[S\u00e1bado Gigante]], Showbiz (CNNEspa\u00f1ol) or Amigas y Conocidas (TVE) , among many others. She has been a special collaborator in publications such as [[Publimetro]], Huffington Post or [https://www.glamour.mx/tu-vida/descubre/articulos/las-fobias-mas-comunes/10197 Glamour M\u00e9xico.]\n\nSilvia has written five books about love, sex, self-esteem and emotions. They are titled \"''[https://www.amazon.es/Preguntale-Silvia-Los-Secretos-Eva/dp/6071101492 Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva]''\" (Aguilar, 2009), \"[https://www.amazon.es/Misterios-Amor-Sexo-Mysteries-Love/dp/6071106370/ref=sr_1_3?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1445700925&sr=1-3 Los misterios del amor y el sexo]\" (Aguilar, 2010), \"[https://www.amazon.es/MIS-Sentimientos-Erroneos-Silvia-Olmedo/dp/6071130689/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1445700934&sr=1-1 Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos]\" (Aguilar, 2014) and \"''[https://www.amazon.com.mx/emocional-Edici%C3%B3n-mexicana-Silvia-Olmedo-ebook/dp/B01LZ00RTS/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1478197086&sr=8-1&keywords=detox+emocional Detox emocional (Saca de tu vida lo que te hace infeliz)]\"''  (Days of Today, 2016) ando [https://www.amazon.com/dos-pasos-locura-Steps-Madness \"A dos pasos de la locura\"] (Aguilar, 2018). All her books have been best sellers, all of them with more than 4 reprints and an initial output of 20,000 copies. She has presented her books at important fairs such as [[:es:Feria Internacional del Libro de Guadalajara (M\u00e9xico)|The International Book Fair of Guadalajara]], [[:es:Feria Internacional del Libro del Palacio de Miner\u00eda|The International Book Fair of Palacio de la Miner\u00eda,]] and the [http://www.udgusa.org/udgla/proyectos-estrategicos/leala-feria-del-libro-en-espanol-de-los-angeles Spanish Book Fair in Los Angeles].\n\nIn addition to her work in television, Silvia is dedicated to research on physical, mental and emotional health issues. She was a member of the editorial board of Women's Health magazine, collaborates with various NGOs such as Mexico Vivo for HIV education and prevention and belongs to the Vive Consciente steering committee that fights against cervical cancer and the human papillomavirus. She is also a recognized lecturer.\n\nIn May 2019, the program [http://desdepuebla.com/2019/05/22/rocio-sanchez-azuara-es-la-conductora-de-la-tercera-en-discordia-el-nuevo-talk-show-televisivo/ \"La tercera en discordia\"] was premiered in Unicable, [https://www.unicable.tv/programas/la-3ra-en-discordia it is an original idea of Silvia Olmedo], produced by [https://twitter.com/Alexis_N_Oliva Alexis N\u00fa\u00f1ez] and presented by [https://twitter.com/RocioSAzuara Roc\u00edo S\u00e1nchez Azuara], which will address current social issues.\n\nIn Spain he has collaborated for various media such as [http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/13/actualidad/1447421801_353636.html LOS40], [http://www.cadenadial.com/autor/silviaolmedo Cadena Dial], [https://elle.mx/tag/silvia-olmedo/ Elle], [https://www.enfemenino.com/consejos/manual-de-primeros-auxilios-para-cenas-familiares-en-navidad-s1677583.html Enfemenino] or [https://smoda.elpais.com/belleza/bienestar/6-pasos-desintoxicarte-emocionalmente/ El Pa\u00eds.]\n\n==Television shows==\n\n*[https://www.unicable.tv/programas/terapia-de-shock/ Terapia de Shock], 2019 - today. Unicable. Televisa Networks\n*''[https://www.unicable.tv/programas/mind-sex/clip/que-es-el-acoso-sexual Mindsex]'', 2018. Unicable, Televisa Networks.\n*''[https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhU0y4L0hIUwtcoQdWnfiqEMD_hkLvhqO Amordidas]'' 2013 \u2013 2018 Unicable, Televisa Networks\n*''Cuentamelove'' 2007 - 2014 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Sexo Consentido''. 2009 - 2011 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Sexo con Kristoff'' 2006 - 2009 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Picnic. 2004-2006 -'' Telehit, Televisa Networks,\n\n==Radio==\n* ''\u00cdntimamente''. 2012 MVS 102.5\n\n==Books==\n\n**''Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva''  (''Ask Silvia\u2026Eve's secrets'') (Aguilar, 2009)\n** ''Los misterios del amor y el sexo'' (''The Mysteries of Love and Sex)'' (Aguilar, 2010)\n** ''Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos'' ''(My Wrong Feeling)'' (Aguilar, 2014)\n** ''Detox emocional (Saca de tu vida lo que te hace infeliz)'' (D\u00edas de Hoy, 2016)\n**''A dos pasos de la locura''  ''(Two steps of Madness)'' (Aguilar, 2018)\n\n==Honors==\n\nIn November 2010, Silvia Olmedo was awarded in Los Angeles, CA by Premios Libertad and One Love Foundation; winning the categories of Most Popular TV Show for ''Cuentamelove'' and Most Popular Informative TV Show Host.<ref>http://latinola.com/story.php?story=8980/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\nIn 2012 One of the Year (For her work on health promotion and psychology by the Women Mexican Chamber of Commerce)\n\nNamed Health Ambassador in Social Networks by Mexico's Ministry of Health.<ref>http://www.cruzrojamexicana.org.mx/?p=2585</ref>\n\n== Appearance and collaboration of Silvia Olmedo in Spanish media ==\n*https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4206818/0/walter-riso-silvia-olmedo-quienes-son-los-autenticos-influencers-de-la-psicologia-en-redes-sociales/\n*http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/13/actualidad/1447421801_353636.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/01/14/love40/1452794093_903132.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/02/03/love40/1454517846_537709.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/03/17/love40/1458214700_533197.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/25/love40/1448455810_057395.html\n* http://www.cadenadial.com/autor/silviaolmedo\n* http://www.enfemenino.com/consejos/manual-de-primeros-auxilios-para-cenas-familiares-en-navidad-s1677583.html#link_time=1449767748\n* http://www.mujeresreales.es/consumo-trabajo/articulo/fiestas-navidenas-de-trabajo-como-actuar-451450711896\n* http://www.elle.es/pareja-sexo/mente-ok/somos-infieles\n* http://www.larazon.es/opinion/columnistas/detox-emocional-DC12679381#.Ttt16Y46YPDkrCk\n* http://www.webconsultas.com/entrevistas/mente-y-emociones/silvia-olmedo-psicologa-y-autora-de-detox-emocional\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/06/14/actualidad/1465888706_735220.html\n* http://smoda.elpais.com/belleza/bienestar/6-pasos-desintoxicarte-emocionalmente/\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://silviaolmedo.com Sitio web oficial]\n* [https://www.facebook.com/Silvia-Olmedo-55543311406/ Silvia Olmedo on Facebook]\n* [https://www.instagram.com/silviaolmedo/ Silvia Olmedo on Instagram]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBYzEyycSUN_3U4els3LH8A Silvia Olmedo on Youtube]\n* {{Twitter|silviaolmedo}}\n*[[imdbname:3099167|Silvia Olmedo on IMBd]]\n{{commonscat}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Olmedo, Silvia}}\n[[Category:Mexican television talk show hosts]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Popular psychology]]\n[[Category:People from Madrid]]\n[[Category:Spanish emigrants to Mexico]]\n[[Category:1976 births]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|TV psychologist and author}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Silvia Olmedo\n| image = Silvia Olmedo Psic\u00f3loga.jpg\n| imagesize = \n| caption = \n| birth_name = Silvia Olmedo\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1976|05|16}}\n| birth_place = [[Madrid]], [[Spain]]\n| occupation = Psychologist, television host, [[writer]], [[lecturer]]\n| yearsactive = \n| website = http://silviaolmedo.com\n}}\n\n'''Silvia Olmedo''' (born 16 May 1976) is a [[Spaniards|Spanish]] [[psychologist]], [[sexologist]], [[Television presenter|television host]], [[Television producer|producer]] and [[author]]. She has worked in Spain, [[United States|America]], [[United Kingdom|Britain]], [[Netherlands]], [[Australia]] and [[Mexico]], where she currently hosts a [[television program]] named ''Terapia de Shock''<ref>https://www.canalu.mx/programas/mind-sex</ref> focused on educating people on psychology, sexology and health habits.\n\nSilvia has written five books about psychology, in which she talks about relationships, sexuality, anxiety and self-esteem \u2013 ''Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva'' (''Ask Silvia\u2026Eve's secrets''),<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/preguntale-a-silvia/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> ''Los misterios del amor y el sexo'' (''The Mysteries of Love and Sex'')<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>'', Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos''.,<ref>http://www.librosaguilar.com/mx/libro/mis-sentimientos-erroneos/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> ''Detox Emocional''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.planetadelibros.com/libro-detox-emocional/206924}}</ref> and ''A dos pasos de la locura (Two steps from Madness)''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/604963/a-dos-pasos-de-la-locura--two-steps-from-madness-by-silvia-olmedo/9781949061413/}}</ref>''.'' All of them became bestsellers, with more than 150,000 copies sold.<ref>http://www.radioformula.com.mx/notas.asp?Idn=466203&idFC=2014/</ref>\n\nBesides her work as a television [[Content (media)|content]] producer and host, she's also dedicated to research in health and mental issues. Silvia is member of the editorial board of ''Women's Health'' magazine. She collaborates with [[Non-governmental organization|NGOs]] such as M\u00e9xico Vivo for education and HIV prevention and is part of the steering committee of Vive Consciente. She is also a well-known lecturer.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tuxtlaenlinea.com/sitio/eventos-2/conferencia-los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo-por-silvia-olmedo/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-12-29 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229050945/http://tuxtlaenlinea.com/sitio/eventos-2/conferencia-los-misterios-del-amor-y-el-sexo-por-silvia-olmedo/ |archivedate=29 December 2014 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nSilvia Olmedo is a content producer and host since 2006. She started at Telelehit with Cuentamelove. She also appears regularly in programs like [[:es:Hoy (programa de televisi\u00f3n)|Hoy]], [[\u00a1Despierta Am\u00e9rica!|Despierta Am\u00e9rica]] and [[Netas Divinas]]. She has also been invited to Primero Noticias, [[S\u00e1bado Gigante]], Showbiz (CNNEspa\u00f1ol) or Amigas y Conocidas (TVE) , among many others. She has been a special collaborator in publications such as [[Publimetro]], Huffington Post or [https://www.glamour.mx/tu-vida/descubre/articulos/las-fobias-mas-comunes/10197 Glamour M\u00e9xico.]\n\nSilvia has written five books about love, sex, self-esteem and emotions. They are titled \"''[https://www.amazon.es/Preguntale-Silvia-Los-Secretos-Eva/dp/6071101492 Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva]''\" (Aguilar, 2009), \"[https://www.amazon.es/Misterios-Amor-Sexo-Mysteries-Love/dp/6071106370/ref=sr_1_3?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1445700925&sr=1-3 Los misterios del amor y el sexo]\" (Aguilar, 2010), \"[https://www.amazon.es/MIS-Sentimientos-Erroneos-Silvia-Olmedo/dp/6071130689/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1445700934&sr=1-1 Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos]\" (Aguilar, 2014) and \"''[https://www.amazon.com.mx/emocional-Edici%C3%B3n-mexicana-Silvia-Olmedo-ebook/dp/B01LZ00RTS/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1478197086&sr=8-1&keywords=detox+emocional Detox emocional (Saca de tu vida lo que te hace infeliz)]\"''  (Days of Today, 2016) ando [https://www.amazon.com/dos-pasos-locura-Steps-Madness \"A dos pasos de la locura\"] (Aguilar, 2018). All her books have been best sellers, all of them with more than 4 reprints and an initial output of 20,000 copies. She has presented her books at important fairs such as [[:es:Feria Internacional del Libro de Guadalajara (M\u00e9xico)|The International Book Fair of Guadalajara]], [[:es:Feria Internacional del Libro del Palacio de Miner\u00eda|The International Book Fair of Palacio de la Miner\u00eda,]] and the [http://www.udgusa.org/udgla/proyectos-estrategicos/leala-feria-del-libro-en-espanol-de-los-angeles Spanish Book Fair in Los Angeles].\n\nIn addition to her work in television, Silvia is dedicated to research on physical, mental and emotional health issues. She was a member of the editorial board of Women's Health magazine, collaborates with various NGOs such as Mexico Vivo for HIV education and prevention and belongs to the Vive Consciente steering committee that fights against cervical cancer and the human papillomavirus. She is also a recognized lecturer.\n\nIn May 2019, the program [http://desdepuebla.com/2019/05/22/rocio-sanchez-azuara-es-la-conductora-de-la-tercera-en-discordia-el-nuevo-talk-show-televisivo/ \"La tercera en discordia\"] was premiered in Unicable, [https://www.unicable.tv/programas/la-3ra-en-discordia it is an original idea of Silvia Olmedo], produced by [https://twitter.com/Alexis_N_Oliva Alexis N\u00fa\u00f1ez] and presented by [https://twitter.com/RocioSAzuara Roc\u00edo S\u00e1nchez Azuara], which will address current social issues.\n\nIn Spain he has collaborated for various media such as [http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/13/actualidad/1447421801_353636.html LOS40], [http://www.cadenadial.com/autor/silviaolmedo Cadena Dial], [https://elle.mx/tag/silvia-olmedo/ Elle], [https://www.enfemenino.com/consejos/manual-de-primeros-auxilios-para-cenas-familiares-en-navidad-s1677583.html Enfemenino] or [https://smoda.elpais.com/belleza/bienestar/6-pasos-desintoxicarte-emocionalmente/ El Pa\u00eds.]\n\n==Television shows==\n\n*[https://www.unicable.tv/programas/terapia-de-shock/ Terapia de Shock], 2019 - today. Unicable. Televisa Networks\n*''[https://www.unicable.tv/programas/mind-sex/clip/que-es-el-acoso-sexual Mindsex]'', 2018. Unicable, Televisa Networks.\n*''[https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhU0y4L0hIUwtcoQdWnfiqEMD_hkLvhqO Amordidas]'' 2013 \u2013 2018 Unicable, Televisa Networks\n*''Cuentamelove'' 2007 - 2014 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Sexo Consentido''. 2009 - 2011 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Sexo con Kristoff'' 2006 - 2009 Telehit, Televisa Networks\n*''Picnic. 2004-2006 -'' Telehit, Televisa Networks,\n\n==Radio==\n* ''\u00cdntimamente''. 2012 MVS 102.5\n\n==Books==\n\n**''Preg\u00fantale a Silvia\u2026Los secretos de Eva''  (''Ask Silvia\u2026Eve's secrets'') (Aguilar, 2009)\n** ''Los misterios del amor y el sexo'' (''The Mysteries of Love and Sex)'' (Aguilar, 2010)\n** ''Mis sentimientos err\u00f3neos'' ''(My Wrong Feeling)'' (Aguilar, 2014)\n** ''Detox emocional (Saca de tu vida lo que te hace infeliz)'' (D\u00edas de Hoy, 2016)\n**''A dos pasos de la locura''  ''(Two steps of Madness)'' (Aguilar, 2018)\n\n==Honors==\n\nIn November 2010, Silvia Olmedo was awarded in Los Angeles, CA by Premios Libertad and One Love Foundation; winning the categories of Most Popular TV Show for ''Cuentamelove'' and Most Popular Informative TV Show Host.<ref>http://latinola.com/story.php?story=8980/{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\nIn 2012 One of the Year (For her work on health promotion and psychology by the Women Mexican Chamber of Commerce)\n\nNamed Health Ambassador in Social Networks by Mexico's Ministry of Health.<ref>http://www.cruzrojamexicana.org.mx/?p=2585</ref>\n\n== Appearance and collaboration of Silvia Olmedo in Spanish media ==\n* http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/13/actualidad/1447421801_353636.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/01/14/love40/1452794093_903132.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/02/03/love40/1454517846_537709.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/03/17/love40/1458214700_533197.html\n* http://los40.com/los40/2015/11/25/love40/1448455810_057395.html\n* http://www.cadenadial.com/autor/silviaolmedo\n* http://www.enfemenino.com/consejos/manual-de-primeros-auxilios-para-cenas-familiares-en-navidad-s1677583.html#link_time=1449767748\n* http://www.mujeresreales.es/consumo-trabajo/articulo/fiestas-navidenas-de-trabajo-como-actuar-451450711896\n* http://www.elle.es/pareja-sexo/mente-ok/somos-infieles\n* http://www.larazon.es/opinion/columnistas/detox-emocional-DC12679381#.Ttt16Y46YPDkrCk\n* http://www.webconsultas.com/entrevistas/mente-y-emociones/silvia-olmedo-psicologa-y-autora-de-detox-emocional\n* http://los40.com/los40/2016/06/14/actualidad/1465888706_735220.html\n* http://smoda.elpais.com/belleza/bien