i.mcgill.ca/RASI/BEA/Ibn_al-Haytham_BEA.pdf PDF version])\n* {{Cite encyclopedia |first= A. I. |last= Sabra |author-link= A. I. Sabra |date= 2008 |orig-year= 1970\u201380 |title= Ibn Al-Haytham, Ab\u016b \u02bfAl\u012b Al-\u1e24asan Ibn Al-\u1e24asan |encyclopedia= [[Dictionary of Scientific Biography|Complete Dictionary of Scientific Biography]] |publisher= Charles Scribner's Sons |url= http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G2-2830901904.html }}\n* [http://www.muslimheritage.com/article/nader-el-bizri-ibn-al-haytham-introduction 'A Brief Introduction on Ibn al-Haytham' based on a lecture delivered at the Royal Society in London by Nader El-Bizri]\n* [http://www-personal.umich.edu/~jbourj/money4.htm Ibn al-Haytham on two Iraqi banknotes]\n* [http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0014/001412/141236E.pdf The Miracle of Light&nbsp;\u2013 a UNESCO article on Ibn al-Haytham]\n* [http://www.malaspina.org/alhazen.htm Biography from Malaspina Global Portal]\n* [http://www.amaana.org/ISWEB/contents.htm#pos9 Short biographies on several \"Muslim Heroes and Personalities\" including Ibn al-Haytham]\n* {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/19991013041615/http://www.ionet.net/~usarch/WTB-Services/MiddleEast/WTB-ME-Thinkers-IbnAlHaitham.shtml |date=13 October 1999 |title=Biography from ioNET }}\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/alhazen.shtml |title=Biography from the BBC |accessdate=16 September 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060211032459/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/alhazen.shtml |archivedate=11 February 2006 |df= }}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080708215144/http://www.trincoll.edu/depts/phil/philo/phils/muslim/alhazen.html Biography from Trinity College (Connecticut)]\n* [http://micro.magnet.fsu.edu/optics/timeline/people/alhazen.html Biography from Molecular Expressions]\n* [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7810846.stm The First True Scientist] from BBC News\n* [http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0021/0