uces its First Thin Film Solar Panel | publisher= Solarbuzz |date=7 September 2009}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-18\">{{cite web |url= http://investor.firstsolar.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=201491&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1328913&highlight= |title= First Solar to Team With Ordos City on Major Solar Power Plant in China Desert |publisher= First Solar |date= 8 September 2009 |url-status= dead |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200413/http://investor.firstsolar.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=201491&p=irol-newsarticle&id=1328913&highlight= |archivedate= 3 March 2016 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-21\">[http://www.worldbiofuelssymposium.com/2005FEW-01-Liu.pdf Chinese development status of bioethanol and biodiesel]</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-22\">[http://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/weo/2007/update/01/index.htm World Economic Outlook Update], 25 July 2007</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-23\">[http://www.chinastrategiesllc.com/PDFs/Bioenergy%20Business%20June%202007%20China.pdf Sector looks set to grow to be pillar of economy]</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-24\">{{cite web |url=http://www.ashdenawards.org/winners/daxu |title=Daxu, stoves burning crop waste |author=Ashden Awards |accessdate=2008-11-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215103233/http://www.ashdenawards.org/winners/daxu |archivedate=2009-02-15 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-25\">{{cite web |url=http://www.ashdenawards.org/winners/shaanxi |title=Shaanxi Mothers, biogas for cooking and lighting |author=Ashden Awards |accessdate=2008-11-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211142339/http://www.ashdenawards.org/winners/shaanxi |archivedate=2008-12-11 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-26\">[http://www.bl-a.com/ECB/PDFFiles/China1996.PDF Geothermal Resources in China]</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-27\">{{cite web|url=http://finance.qq.com/a/20100130/002100.htm|title=\u56fd\u5bb6\u80fd\u6e90\u90e8\u96cf\u5f62\u521d\u73b0 \u6298\u5c04\u4e2d\u56fd\u80fd\u6e90\u683c\u5c40\u6df7\u4e71|publisher=|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-28\">{{cite web|url=http://news.163.com/10/0127/16/5U21LI7V0001124J.html|title=\u56fd\u5bb6\u80fd\u6e90\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a\u6210\u7acb \u6e29\u5bb6\u5b9d\u4efb\u4e3b\u4efb|author=\u7f51\u6613|publisher=|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-29\">{{cite news|title=US Replaces China as Top Clean Energy Investor|url=http://www.environmentalleader.com/2012/01/17/us-replaces-china-as-top-clean-energy-investor/|newspaper=Environmental Leader}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-30\">{{cite web|url=http://www.china.com.cn/chinese/law/798072.htm|title=\u4e2d\u534e\u4eba\u6c11\u5171\u548c\u56fd\u53ef\u518d\u751f\u80fd\u6e90\u6cd5(\u5168\u6587)|publisher=|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-31\">{{cite web|url=http://www.newenergy.org.cn/html/01010/10231036612.html|title=\u53ef\u518d\u751f\u80fd\u6e90\u5341\u4e8c\u4e94\u89c4\u5212\u521d\u7a3f\u62df\u5b9a \u6c34\u7535\u6838\u7535\u9886\u8854\u65b0\u80fd\u6e90|publisher=|accessdate=17 December 2016}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-32\">{{cite web|url=http://www.china.com.cn/policy/txt/2009-07/23/content_18186602.htm|title=\u91d1\u592a\u9633\u793a\u8303\u5de5\u7a0b\u8d22\u653f\u8865\u52a9\u8d44\u91d1\u7ba1\u7406\u6682\u884c\u529e\u6cd5(\u5168\u6587)|publisher=|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-33\">[http://www.in-en.com/newenergy/policy/china/2007/03/INEN_75292.html \u53d1\u6539\u59d4\u5173\u4e8e\u4fc3\u8fdb\u98ce\u7535\u4ea7\u4e1a\u53d1\u5c55\u5b9e\u65bd\u610f\u89c1]</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-34\">{{cite web|url=http://www.china.com.cn/chinese/law/798072.htm|title=\u4e2d\u534e\u4eba\u6c11\u5171\u548c\u56fd\u53ef\u518d\u751f\u80fd\u6e90\u6cd5|publisher=|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-35\">[http://www.hbsafety.cn/article/318/320/201002/69453.shtml\u6c34\u7535\u7ad9\u5927\u575d\u8fd0\u884c\u5b89\u5168\u7ba1\u7406\u89c4\u5b9a]</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-36\">[http://www.newenergy.org.cn/html/0066/2006620_10460.html\u